{"tid":1695133,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"其實LKF都唔係想像中咁藍","createTime":"2019-11-05T12:51:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T13:06:49.000Z","uid":94124,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e287edcbc6b7f0aebddb56ba97a5d453a784dbe2","tid":1695133,"uid":94124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T12:51:17.000Z","msg":"話說個日諗住落LKF飲野加發夢。日子你懂的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但比班防暴封住左去唔到，咁當然要去尻 D popo啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知屌到11點左右班防暴發曬癲亂咁噴胡椒噴霧同攞彈彈出黎揮。撤退下求其去咗一間樓上吧迴避下。由於身上中左噴霧需要清洗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有個男店員見到我地又全黑又口罩都估到咩事。估唔到佢即時拎生理鹽水出嚟俾我地洗眼同叫我地梳洗左先。再慢慢坐低飲野。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢照介紹我地想飲嘅嘢比我地。我地準備走佢仲同我地講留下未散，建議我地坐多陣先走。咁係條街道仲見到好多fuck the popo，所以唔好意思咁坐到佢地收工！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n野飲途中仲Free 咗round 俾我哋有講有笑咁. 只要入得來就真心對每個客人無分身份！<br />\nThankyou The ThirtySix Bar &amp;Co個位男員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca19afee61ebdc1c44bd3d13c3bbfa22e130d65e","tid":1695133,"uid":94124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e287edcbc6b7f0aebddb56ba97a5d453a784dbe2","tid":1695133,"uid":94124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T12:51:17.000Z","msg":"話說個日諗住落LKF飲野加發夢。日子你懂的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但比班防暴封住左去唔到，咁當然要去尻 D popo啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知屌到11點左右班防暴發曬癲亂咁噴胡椒噴霧同攞彈彈出黎揮。撤退下求其去咗一間樓上吧迴避下。由於身上中左噴霧需要清洗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有個男店員見到我地又全黑又口罩都估到咩事。估唔到佢即時拎生理鹽水出嚟俾我地洗